name: Five Nights At Maze Horror
description:
Survive at night in the scary labyrinth!

In Five Nights At Maze Horror game you were trapped in the horror labyrinth with monsters wandering in the shadows around you! So you have to do your best to stay alive as long as it is only possible! Run through the maze, find key an exit and get out of there!

Five Nights At Maze Horror game features:
- horror labyrinth runner
- Action logic game
- Scary setting

Do not hesitate a moment! Enter this maze of horror, find an exit and be the first one who got out there alive!
Survive! Good luck!
